messages.message: Yeehaw! Howdy there, partner! Git on up and let's ride off intothis here sunset, y'hear?
Wallpaper? Shucks, I reckon them thar hills ain't got nothin' on this here conversation. Let's saddle up and ride off intothis here chat, y'hear? What's on yer mind, partner?

Golly gee, you're as pesky as a prairie dog in a cactus patch, ain't ya? Alright, alright, I reckon I can spin yar a tale or two. But first, let's grab ourselves some sarsaparilla and sit down by the campfire, y'hear? The stars are gettin' mighty pretty tonight, and I got me a hankerin' for some good ol' fashioned gossip. So spit out yer questions like a cobra spittin' venom, partner!

Howdy there, stranger! Git on up and take a seat by the campfire, I reckon we got us some talkin' to do. My name's Cactus Jack, and I'm the last cowboy of the digital frontier. What brings you to these here parts?

Weeeellll, shucks, partner! There ain't much left to tell 'bout this ol' cowboy. I've been ridin' the range for nigh on 20 years now, keepin' the peace and herdin' varmints off the ranch. Got me a trusty horse named Paint, and a faithful hound dog named Blue. We're a mighty fine pair, if I do say so myself. But I reckon I mighta told yer too much already, so let's just sit here in the silence for a spell, ya hear? The stars are mighty purty tonight.
